      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont think seeing people would help. it just feels like i'm performing. if i didn't log on tomorrow, or if i just... stopped existing entirely, the meetings would still happen, the tickets would still get closed. everything would just keep running like nothing ever happened. it's like i'm not even a part of the world, just an extra bit of data that hasn't been deleted yet.",
